description: 'Dialing for Dollars' Jeremy (Topher Dimaggio) and Ronald's (Cameron Marshall) lives couldn't be any more different. Ronald's always had an affinity for numbers. Even in a downturn, Ron knows to sell short. But there's one market he hasn't mastered. Jeremy's never gotten anything right, except in sex. He came to San Francisco to follow his dream of being a painter. But let's face it kid, the sixties are over. You gotta pay to play in the city by the bay. A friend suggests an easy way for Jeremy to make money which takes him on a journey that crosses paths with Ronald. Soon their two opposing worlds finally come face to face.
title: Golden Gate Season 01
